nftables 

sudo nft list ruleset

Add port
sudo nft add rule inet filter input tcp dport 80 accept
sudo nft add rule inet filter input udp dport 1194 accept
sudo nft add rule inet filter input ip saddr 192.168.1.100 tcp dport 22 accept
sudo nft list ruleset > /etc/nftables.conf
sudo systemctl enable --now nftables

sudo netstat -tulnp | grep LISTEN

remove port
sudo nft list table inet filter
sudo nft delete rule inet filter input handle <rule_number>

to add rule
nft add rule inet filter input iifname enp7s0 oifname docker0 tcp dport 443 accept
nft add rule inet filter input iifname enp7s0 tcp dport 443 dnat to 172.19.0.3:443


